The native adapter in this directory (adapter.m, loader.pl) ports techniques
from two projects by Jonas van den Berg:

  ungive/mediaremote-adapter — https://github.com/ungive/mediaremote-adapter
      Source of the perl-loader + Objective-C MediaRemote technique.
      Licensed under the BSD 3-Clause License (LICENSE file present).

  ungive/media-control — https://github.com/ungive/media-control
      Referenced only for CLI command naming and JSON field conventions.
      It declares the BSD 3-Clause License in its README but ships no
      standalone LICENSE file; its adapter code is the mediaremote-adapter
      repository included as a git submodule.

