The MediaRemote private-framework symbol names and command IDs are documented
in davidmurray/ios-reversed-headers (MediaRemote.h). The JXA fallback
technique (scripts/read-jxa.js) follows the public gist by SKaplanOfficial and
fastfetch's implementation.
